description: Strengthening Early Recovery for Comprehensive & Sustainable Reintegration of IDPs

subproject.description: The project supports the National Recovery Strategy. It comes as a response to reintegration monitoring reports that highlighted the lack of suitable community infrastructure in communities where displaced people have resettled and tensions arising from competition on scarce resources. It supports the reintegration process by (1) developing small community infrastructure using an inclusive and participatory approach, and (2) supporting Early Recovery coordination.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Support to reintegration
